6毛口罩卖1元被罚4万，洪湖市监局：指导意见冲突将讨论。
6 Mask sold for 1 yuan was fined 40,000, Honghu City Supervision Bureau: the conflict of guidance will be discussed.
赵孟。
Zhao Meng.
界面新闻                      。
Interface news.
界面新闻。
